deviceTable.name: deviceTable
deviceTable.description: This table describes the device-status of the CWDM-system.

deviceTableEntry.name: deviceTableEntry
deviceTableEntry.description: An entry in the port table.

deviceId.name: deviceId
deviceId.description: This entry describes the device id.

deviceArtNo.name: deviceArtNo
deviceArtNo.description: This entry describes the article number of the device.

deviceSerNo.name: deviceSerNo
deviceSerNo.description: This entry describes the serial number of the device.

deviceDesc.name: deviceDesc
deviceDesc.description: This entry provides a detailed description of the device.

deviceTemperature.name: deviceTemperature
deviceTemperature.description: This entry describes the temperature of the device in degree centigrade.

deviceTempAlarmThreshold.name: deviceTempAlarmThreshold
deviceTempAlarmThreshold.description: This entry describes the current temperature-alarm threshold value of the device in degree centigrade.

deviceTempAlarm.name: deviceTempAlarm
deviceTempAlarm.description: This entry describes if a temperature-alarm condition has occurred or not.

deviceTempShutdown.name: deviceTempShutdown
deviceTempShutdown.description: This entry describes if a temperature-shutdown condition has occurred or not.

deviceTrPowerFailureAlarm.name: deviceTrPowerFailureAlarm
deviceTrPowerFailureAlarm.description: This entry describes if a transceiver-board power-supply-alarm condition has occurred or not.

deviceMinorAlarm.name: deviceMinorAlarm
deviceMinorAlarm.description: This entry describes if a minor-alarm condition has occurred or not.

deviceMajorAlarm.name: deviceMajorAlarm
deviceMajorAlarm.description: This entry describes if a major-alarm condition has occurred or not.

portTable.name: portTable
portTable.description: This table describes the port-status of the CWDM-system.

portTableEntry.name: portTableEntry
portTableEntry.description: An entry in the port table.

portId.name: portId
portId.description: This entry describes the port id.

portChannelEnabled.name: portChannelEnabled
portChannelEnabled.description: This entry describes the channel's status. A value of 1 indicates that the channel is enabled, a value of 0 indicates that the channel is not enabled.

portLinkThroughLocalLine.name: portLinkThroughLocalLine
portLinkThroughLocalLine.description: This entry describes the local-line link-through-status of the port.

portLinkThroughLineLocal.name: portLinkThroughLineLocal
portLinkThroughLineLocal.description: This entry describes the line-local link-through-status of the port.

portLocalModuleInstalled.name: portLocalModuleInstalled
portLocalModuleInstalled.description: This entry describes if a local transceiver module is installed or not.

portLineModuleInstalled.name: portLineModuleInstalled
portLineModuleInstalled.description: This entry describes if a line transceiver module is installed or not.

portLocalLink.name: portLocalLink
portLocalLink.description: This entry describes the port's local link status.

portLineLink.name: portLineLink
portLineLink.description: This entry describes the port's line link status.

portLocalTxFault.name: portLocalTxFault
portLocalTxFault.description: This entry describes the port's local-tx-fault status.

portLineTxFault.name: portLineTxFault
portLineTxFault.description: This entry describes the port's line-tx-fault status.

portLocalPowerFault.name: portLocalPowerFault
portLocalPowerFault.description: This entry describes the port's local-power-fault status.

portLinePowerFault.name: portLinePowerFault
portLinePowerFault.description: This entry describes the port's line-power-fault status.

portRateSelect.name: portRateSelect
portRateSelect.description: This entry describes the port's local data rate. A value of 1 describes full data rate, a value of 0 describes reduced data rate.

localModuleTable.name: localModuleTable
localModuleTable.description: This table describes the local module status of the CWDM-system.

localModuleTableEntry.name: localModuleTableEntry
localModuleTableEntry.description: An entry in the local module table.

localModuleId.name: localModuleId
localModuleId.description: This entry describes the local module id.

localModuleConnector.name: localModuleConnector
localModuleConnector.description: This entry describes the connector-type of the port.

localModuleTrCodeSonet.name: localModuleTrCodeSonet
localModuleTrCodeSonet.description: This entry describes the SONET compliance of the transceiver.

localModuleTrCodeGigabit.name: localModuleTrCodeGigabit
localModuleTrCodeGigabit.description: This entry describes the Gigabit Ethernet compliance of the transceiver.

localModuleTrCodeFbLinkLength.name: localModuleTrCodeFbLinkLength
localModuleTrCodeFbLinkLength.description: This entry describes the fibre channel link length of the transceiver.

localModuleTrCodeFbTrTech.name: localModuleTrCodeFbTrTech
localModuleTrCodeFbTrTech.description: This entry describes the fibre channel transmitter technology of the transceiver.

localModuleTrCodeFbTrMedia.name: localModuleTrCodeFbTrMedia
localModuleTrCodeFbTrMedia.description: This entry describes the fibre channel transmission media of the transceiver.

localModuleTrCodeFbSpeed.name: localModuleTrCodeFbSpeed
localModuleTrCodeFbSpeed.description: This entry describes the fibre channel speed of the transceiver.

localModuleBrNominal.name: localModuleBrNominal
localModuleBrNominal.description: This entry describes the nominal bit rate, specified in units of 100 Megabits per second.

localModuleLength9km.name: localModuleLength9km
localModuleLength9km.description: This entry describes the link length supported by the transceiver using single-mode fibers. The value is in units of kilometers. A value of 255 means that the transceiver supports a link length greater than 254 km. A value of zero means that the transceiver does not support single-mode fibers.

localModuleLength9m.name: localModuleLength9m
localModuleLength9m.description: This entry describes the link length supported by the transceiver using single-mode fibers. The value is in units of 100 meters. A value of 255 means that the transceiver supports a link length greater than 25.4 km. A value of zero means that the transceiver does not support single-mode fibers.

localModuleLength50.name: localModuleLength50
localModuleLength50.description: This entry describes the link length supported by the transceiver using 50 micron multi-mode mode fibers. The value is in units of 10 meters. A value of 255 means that the transceiver supports a link length greater than 2.54 km. A value of zero means that the transceiver does not support 50 micron multi-mode fibers.

localModuleLength62.name: localModuleLength62
localModuleLength62.description: This entry describes the link length supported by the transceiver using 62.5 micron multi-mode mode fibers. The value is in units of 10 meters. A value of 255 means that the transceiver supports a link length greater than 2.54 km. A value of zero means that the transceiver does not support 62.5 micron multi-mode fibers.

localModuleLengthCopper.name: localModuleLengthCopper
localModuleLengthCopper.description: This entry describes the link length supported by the transceiver using copper cables. The value is in units of 1 meter. A value of 255 means that the transceiver supports a link length greater than 254 m. A value of zero means that the transceiver does not support copper cables.

localModuleVendorSN.name: localModuleVendorSN
localModuleVendorSN.description: This entry describes the vendor's serial number of the transceiver.

localModuleDateCode.name: localModuleDateCode
localModuleDateCode.description: This entry describes the vendor's date code in the [yymmdd]-format.

localModuleLaserCurrent.name: localModuleLaserCurrent
localModuleLaserCurrent.description: This entry describes the transmitter laser's bias current in milli ampere.

localModuleTransmittedPower.name: localModuleTransmittedPower
localModuleTransmittedPower.description: This entry describes the transmitter optical output power in micro watt.

localModuleReceivedPower.name: localModuleReceivedPower
localModuleReceivedPower.description: This entry describes the transmitter optical received power in micro watt.

localModuleLaserTemperature.name: localModuleLaserTemperature
localModuleLaserTemperature.description: This entry describes the laser temperature in degree centigrade.

localModuleVoltage.name: localModuleVoltage
localModuleVoltage.description: This entry describes the transceiver supply voltage in mV.
